title: Keto Crazy
description:
This week, Jillian digs deep into the science of keto to determine if the benefits are worth the risks. Plus, Dr. Axe is back to help us figure out what supplements we should be taking and why. And the crew decides to live with no regrets and wants you to do so with them!
